========================================================================
What is erlusb?
===============

Erlusb is just a test to see how to interface libusb to Erlang.


========================================================================
How do I build it?
==================

  $ autoreconf -Wall -Werror -ivs
  $ mkdir _b && cd _b
  $ ../configure --prefix=$PWD/../_i
  $ make all check install installcheck


========================================================================
What is the license?
====================

No idea (yet). The complex2.erl and stuff are from the Erlang docs,
anyway.


========================================================================
End of README.
==============
